<h1 style="font-size:24px; line-height:28px; font-weight:bold;display:inline;">南昌航大原党委书记多次召集情妇、妓女搞淫乱活动 <a onclick="addbookmark(window.location,'南昌航大原党委书记多次召集情妇、妓女搞淫乱活动')" style="cursor:pointer;"><img src="/images/dvbbs0/vcopyt.gif" align="absmiddle" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#" id="bbs_go_hwact" style="display:none;" target="_blank"><img src="http://bbs.voc.com.cn/images/bbs_hwact.gif" /></a></h1>
